reviews.author: Selena Harricharan

reviews.title: Good idea
reviews.comment: Guys, the whole point of the game is to explain what we sit here and do all day. Tap tap tap on our phone screens. And what do we get out of it? Nothing. Absolutely nothing. So by tapping the egg and it saying \"So what?\" at the end is soo meaningful. You just have to think about it
reviews.author: Bailey Holcomb

reviews.title: Good but this will be super....
reviews.comment: It is good but I have got a vice from it. Can\'t you add this: for one animal you will need perhaps 100 000. From the egg you will get a random animal perhaps chicken. The point of game will be to have all the animals. But you will also trade animals with friends. Perhaps I have got two chickens and no dog. He has got two dogs but no chickens. So you will trade a dog for chicken. And so on.....
reviews.author: Jergus Krc

reviews.title: No.
reviews.comment: No logical gameplay, just tapping your screen like crazy. Which by the way is not good for your device! Also easy to cheat by connecting to PC.
reviews.author: Veikko Lehtinen

reviews.title: Nothing comes out of the egg!!
reviews.comment: You can set the counter to 1 (on rooted phones) by going to /data/data/com.byebyegame.tamago/files/, and  edit the counter \"saveData.txt\". The egg does nothing, just displays a text at the top saying: \"so what?\"  Thumbs up so people can see!

reviews.comment: I love the feeling that I am accomplishing something that I get by poking my screen over and over. I feel like it should be to a hundred thousand instead of a million
